snippet.title: Wingspan Special Edition - Nintendo Switch Retail Announcement | Signature Edition Games
snippet.description:
❤️ Pre-order Wingspan Special Edition for Nintendo Switch here: https://bit.ly/4aN87rP

Wingspan is the award-winning strategy card game centered around the fascinating world of birds. Suitable for 1 to 5 players, each bird you play unlocks a cascade of potent combinations across your three habitats. 

This special physical edition will include not only the base game but also the European Expansion, Oceania Expansion, and the Seasonal Decorative Pack.

Pre-order Wingspan now to secure your spot among the avian enthusiasts. Don’t miss out!
